      "content": "wait, what? i don't know what you mean by dwarven engineers or goblins. i'm just looking for professional advice on warehouse shrinkage. can you stick to the logistics side?\n\ncan you give me a list of actual, real-world causes for these kinds of small variances in a high-tech warehouse setting? i need to report this to my manager.",
